dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.cbe.project.element.ProjectElementDependency
dataStructure.description:
This allows us to show dependencies, that typically relate to a ProjectElement not being able to commence until another Element has been completed.

This entity is optional
dataStructure.label: ProjectElementDependency

child.name: dependencyType
child.description:
the relationship to be applied between the start or end points of the project elements (refer table 2)

This element is generated from an attribute.

This attribute is optional
child.label: dependencyType

child.name: lead
child.description:

This element is generated from an attribute.

This attribute is optional
child.label: lead

child.name: lag
child.description:
the time lag to be applied to the dependency

This element is generated from an attribute.
